00:00:48,648 --> 00:00:49,842
Jimmy a un ennui, Lois!

18
00:00:51,584 --> 00:00:53,745
M. Meyer, voici mon ami Jerry...

19
00:00:55,855 --> 00:00:57,686
Duncan Meyer.

20
00:00:58,591 --> 00:00:59,649
Vous vous connaissez?

21
